item.title: CVE-2022-43426|2024-08-03T13:32:58.640Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20s3%20explorer%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins S3 Explorer Plugin 1.0.8 and earlier does not mask the AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY form field, increasing the potential for attackers to observe and capture it.
